data.description: This quiet and quaint partially remodeled 3 bed, 1 bath home sits on 3+/- acres and includes water rights and an incredible bonus 4 bed 1 bath remodeled single wide trailer home.  Home is heated via a wood stove and a fuel oil forced air furnace. 2 bedrooms downstairs and 1 up. There is what many would consider a 4th bedroom upstairs as well, but the owners have been using it for an office/storage room. Beautiful, mature yard with large trees, chicken coop, garden spot, some outbuildings and a 2 car garage. There is plenty of room for horses and the pasture is fenced and set up for that. This home is located just South of Moore, right off a paved county maintained road, and in a very rural setting. Perfect for kids and stretching your legs and still close to the amenities of town.
